{"title":"Macworld Podcast 737: Tim Cook and Appleâ€™s sway over privacy, AR, and an Apple Car","link":"https://www.macworld.com/article/342697/macworld-podcast-737-tim-cook-and-apples-sway-over-privacy-ar-and-more.html","date":1617883200000,"content":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/REC-html40/loose.dtd\">\n<html><body><div id=\"link_wrapped_content\">\n<section class=\"wp-block-bigbite-multi-title\"><div class=\"container\"></div></section><p>Apple CEO Tim Cook made some interesting revelations in a recent episode of the &ldquo;Sway&rdquo; podcast. We talk about&nbsp;Cook&rsquo;s comments about&nbsp;privacy, augmented reality,&nbsp;his&nbsp;retirement&nbsp;and more on this episode of the Macworld Podcast.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Before we talk about the Swisher/Cook interview, we talk about Apple&rsquo;s announcement about its Find My program for third-party apps.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>This is episode 737 with&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Jason-Cross/\" target=\"_blank\">Jason Cross</a>,&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Michael-Simon/\" target=\"_blank\">Michael Simon</a>, and&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/author/Roman-Loyola/\" target=\"_blank\">Roman Loyola</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"get-info\">Get info</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>You can listen to Kara Swisher&rsquo;s interview with Tim Cook on the&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/05/opinion/apples-ceo-is-making-very-different-choices-from-mark-zuckerberg.html&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">Sway</a>&nbsp;podcast. The New York Times also has a&nbsp;<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/04/05/opinion/apples-ceo-is-making-very-different-choices-from-mark-zuckerberg.html?showTranscript=1&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" target=\"_blank\">transcript</a>&nbsp;available.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Learn more about <a href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/342763/apple-opens-up-its-find-my-network-to-third-party-devices-no-airtag-needed.html\">Apple&rsquo;s Works with Find My announcement</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"your-hot-takes\">Your hot takes</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>When the interview was released, we posted an article about the part&nbsp;regarding&nbsp;<a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://www.macworld.com/article/342432/tim-cook-not-planning-on-staying-with-apple-through-the-decade.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tim Cook&rsquo;s thoughts on retirement</a>. Macworld readers had some strong opinions.&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">If he leaves Apple the world most be coming to a end in 2 to 4 years and he knows that, so he going to take some kick back time with his family and friends.</p>&mdash; Marvel Jones (@MarvelTuggle) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/MarvelTuggle/status/1379207889156513796?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">April 5, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Y'all&hellip; Tim Cook is SIXTY years young&hellip; you want him to work at Apple till he keels over on top of an iPhone 26 prototype or something?<br><br>Let the man plan a retirement.</p>&mdash; Chris Bucky Barnes (@ChrisBarnesTech) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/ChrisBarnesTech/status/1379174951874408448?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">April 5, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">I&rsquo;m not in love. Jobs&hellip; Jobs I loved.</p>&mdash; The Monocle (@the_monocle) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/the_monocle/status/1379188808671973378?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">April 5, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div></figure><figure class=\"wp-block-embed aligncenter is-type-rich is-provider-twitter wp-block-embed-twitter\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"500\" data-dnt=\"true\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">We love Time cook seriously ? He has no soul</p>&mdash; fightingippo (@fighting_ippo) <a href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com/?id=111346X1569486&amp;url=https://twitter.com/fighting_ippo/status/1379174498004516874?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw&amp;xcust=1-1-342697-0-0-0&amp;sref=https://www.macworld.com/feed\" rel=\"nofollow\">April 5, 2021</a></blockquote><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></div></figure><div class=\"extendedBlock-wrapper block-coreImage center\"><div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" wid